{"nodes": [{"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_06_icones_mascara_moeda_design_icones_mascara_moeda", "label": "\u00cdcones minimalistas + m\u00e1scara de moeda", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-06-icones-mascara-moeda-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Cara profissional: substituir todos os emojis por \u00edcones SVG de linha (estilo Lucide) e formatar valores de dinheiro ao vivo (2000000 \u2192 R$ 2.000.000,00). Est\u00e9tica dark atual intoc\u00e1vel \u2014 decis\u00e3o do pai. Teste e2e varre a p\u00e1gina com regex de faixas Unicode pra garantir zero emoji."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_06_icones_mascara_moeda_design_icones_svg_embutidos", "label": "\u00cdcones SVG embutidos (icons.js, estilo Lucide)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-06-icones-mascara-moeda-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "SVG embutido no site (sem CDN, sem fonte de \u00edcones) \u2014 obrigat\u00f3rio porque o PWA offline s\u00f3 cacheia assets locais. stroke=currentColor mant\u00e9m as classes de cor existentes mandando na cor; nada de cor nova. icons.js entra na lista ASSETS do sw.js."}, {"id": "icons_icon", "label": "ICON(nome, cls) (icons.js)", "file_type": "code", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-06-icones-mascara-moeda-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "app_maskmoney", "label": "maskMoney(input) (app.js)", "file_type": "code", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-06-icones-mascara-moeda-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "M\u00e1scara \u00e9 s\u00f3 apresenta\u00e7\u00e3o: o value do input carrega 2.000.000,00, que o parser atual (app.js:62) j\u00e1 entende; n\u00famero continua n\u00famero no blob salvo. Prefixo R$ fixo fora do valor digit\u00e1vel. Fun\u00e7\u00e3o \u00fanica aplicada a cada campo de dinheiro (#fVal, #fEst, #simValor) na cria\u00e7\u00e3o do modal \u2014 sem duplica\u00e7\u00e3o por modal."}], "edges": [{"source": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_06_icones_mascara_moeda_design_icones_mascara_moeda", "target": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_06_icones_mascara_moeda_design_icones_svg_embutidos", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-06-icones-mascara-moeda-design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_06_icones_mascara_moeda_design_icones_mascara_moeda", "target": "app_maskmoney", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-06-icones-mascara-moeda-design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "icons_icon", "target": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_06_icones_mascara_moeda_design_icones_svg_embutidos", "relation": "implements", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-06-icones-mascara-moeda-design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_06_icones_mascara_moeda_design_icones_mascara_moeda", "target": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_08_afazeres_obra_design_bump_do_service_worker", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-06-icones-mascara-moeda-design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}], "hyperedges": []}